creator: e-nettet
descriptionHtml:
The NemID code app supplements the existing NemID code card enabling you to use NemID directly on your smartphone and tablet.

The NemID code app supports your access to online banking, borger.dk, sundhed.dk and all other websites where you would use your NemID code card.

The app is, after initiation, accessed with a four-digit code or fingerprint recognition.

For security reasons the NemID code app can not be run on rooted smartphones and tablets.

The Danish banks and the Danish public sector are responsible for the NemID code app.

The NemID code app is developed by e-nettet A/S. Nets A/S supplies the infrastructure.
For support please visit: www.nemid.nu
